HEADWORD: Kusimanse
<hw>Ku`si*man"se</hw> <pr>(?)</pr>, <pos>n.</pos> <fld>(Zool.)</fld>
<def>A carnivorous animal (<spn>Crossarchus obscurus</spn>) of tropical
Africa. It its allied to the civets. Called also
<altname>kusimansel</altname>, and <altname>mangue</altname>.</def>⟦br⟧
[<source>1913 Webster</source>]</p>

<p><ent>Kuskus</ent>⟦br⟧
